    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but buyers should come in with realistic expectations. The exterior shows noticeable wear including visible scratches, scuffs, and minor dents consistent with years of regular use. The interior is functional but worn, with fading on surfaces and some minor damage to upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and drives without major issues, though it may benefit from some deferred maintenance and attention to smaller repairs. This is a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer who wants reliable transportation and doesn't mind a car that shows its age. A pre-purchase inspection is encouraged so you know exactly what you're getting.",
